{"tid":1093020,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個發個最奇怪嘅夢","createTime":"2019-04-05T09:47:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-06T02:06:36.000Z","uid":99568,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"dfc4f003e210f8dcf7c792d89543931a75129265","tid":1093020,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T09:47:48.000Z","msg":"呢個夢係我小學嗰陣發生嘅<br />\n不過我諗我呢一世都唔會唔記得<br />\n<br />\n我講番個背景先<br />\n<br />\n我以前小學成日返教會<br />\n自從我知道咗有地獄呢個概念之後我就好驚因為我驚落地獄會被火燒永世永永遠遠比火燒永不超生<br />\n<br />\n所以我發嘅夢就係我全家人諗住上一架通往天堂嘅火車之類嘅物體, 不過正當我上車之前有個人截停咗我話唔畀我上車我唔可以上天堂我要落地獄<br />\n<br />\n原來截停我嗰個人就係mc Jin<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都唔知點解會係mc Jin"},{"pid":"3bd0e8070c62ee8632a2ec98ae28665298a6d8c0","tid":1093020,"uid":99568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T09:48:53.000Z","msg":"真人真事"},{"pid":"c44d02daa60b2638e64bc2b792304ae0c2a76e27","tid":1093020,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T09:49:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"009abef8f45a8536bda6f7b2ced429871571cab4","tid":1093020,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T09:49:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dc4ee418c982a23f73eb3f33623fc15d17bb2a2","tid":1093020,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T09:51:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4c478859e995405a6f8c647dcbc6a12c3cdc508","tid":1093020,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T09:51:27.000Z","msg":"lush"},{"pid":"b7b1a4cb5434a056d0b60a90f8d56a65ae1a6c74","tid":1093020,"uid":181581,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T09:51:32.000Z","msg":"我以前小學成日返教會<br />\n自從我知道咗有地獄呢個概念之後我就好high因為我知落地獄會被火燒永世永永遠遠比火燒永不超生<br />\n<br />\n所以我發嘅夢就