"uid":169832,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T10:11:16.000Z","msg":"都係小學<br />\n 我夢到 我個friend係咁攞啲夾<br />\n（ 黑色小細夾 ）去插我 <br />\n之後我係咁走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再夢到我老母斬撚死佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n 勁驚老母要坐監<br />\n喊醒咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T11:32:45.000Z","msg":"笑撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"633ea605ba2aef1f9e120d39835f537ad276aa63","tid":1093020,"uid":34052,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T15:19:20.000Z","msg":"小學時發嘅夢<br />\n好簡單，就係夢見幾個後生仔女(比我嘅感覺係大家都識)同一個唔知係邊的地方，果時我係幫佢哋影緊相，咁就完左，醒左仲記得，就會覺得好奇怪，又唔係我識嘅小學同學，心諗:既然大家係識嘅點解唔一齊影相，俾着我一定會一齊影。<br />\n<br />\n其實咁就已經完左<br />\n<br />\n事隔好耐，都係近呢幾年發生，同班中學FD去日本旅行，第一次去日本旅行，係咁影影影，當日都唔例外，我幫班FD係JR出口影相，突然比我諗返小學曾經發過既夢，有種似曾相識嘅感覺，果一刻唔知點解覺得好撚恐怖，心諗:快啲影完就走，亦都冇好似細個咁諗一齊影返張相<br />\n<br />\n當日返到酒店開返張相出黎睇嘅時間，有種好奇妙同奇怪嘅感覺唔知點形容，心諗:呢個世界係咪真係有命運呢樣野"},{"pid":"160a80d67ae4734beb9c706f01fc7268e37bd8c9","tid":1093020,"uid":120942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T15:29:17.000Z","msg":"嗰陣細個窮，瞓碌架床，發夢見到小次郎同武藏瞓咗係上面，睇寵物小精靈睇上腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ffda7b665518e4ec01ba05f8809a3c25bbe560c","tid":1093020,"uid":141871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"160a80d67ae4734beb9c706f01fc7268e37bd8c9","tid":1093020,"uid":120942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T15:29:17.000Z","msg":"嗰陣細個窮，瞓碌架床，發夢見到小次郎同武藏瞓咗係上面，睇寵物小精靈睇上腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T15:35:58.000Z","msg":"真人樣定卡通樣"},{"pid":"03475725d0553ebec267323d92d31bdc66684974","tid":1093020,"uid":867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T16:11:15.000Z","msg":"18歲生日果日發夢阿媽死左仲要瞻仰遺容果陣見到佢佢頸都係密集點點<br />\n醒果下喊哂打比佢 佢一聽就話生日快樂呀 我聽到佢把聲喊得仲勁 話好彩你冇死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de94cec81f1770dbf77de46f5e3c5df2566fd33e","tid":1093020,"uid":119007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T16:24:45.000Z","msg":"細個發夢見到3k黨集體行刑，腦海係咁聽到好清晰既慘叫聲同佢地個樣既close up<br />\n直到扎醒之後仲會聽到少少回音<br />\n果陣我仲未知咩係3k黨，淨係記得三角高帽<br />\n之後睇電視知道有呢樣野之後覺得好心寒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5ba59a0a240435ea0d3812acc9b85f1b8c0a6ec","tid":1093020,"uid":4563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T02:06:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />細過成日睇超人<br />\n夢見自己變左超人 然後打怪獸"}]}